</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bkSTSn iEaWBl pf-84_">It raises visibility of the challenges autistic individuals face daily in accessing education, employment, and healthcare.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bkSTSn iEaWBl pf-86_">It inspires change, promoting more inclusive policies, practices, and attitudes.
</li></ul><p class="sc-dPZUdm eeluBw pf-88_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-5d2eb866-d3c7-4197-ac1c-7fa6a5d935fc"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">This day helps us pause, reflect, and recommit to building a world where neurodiversity is understood and valued.
</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-91_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fsvrPk ezIRGP pf-92_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-ePDMnc jGJiiy pf-93_">2025 Theme - “Embracing difference: Shaping inclusive futures”
